grow_vertical = 2
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("1_dbpbn")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 26
text = "In the Bakening, there were four beings, known as C.H.E.Fs (Culinary Harbingers of Extraordinary Finedining). These beings were foretold to bring peace to the world through harmony amongst all taste buds, regardless of ingredients, recipes, and utensils. While 3 of the CHEFs were slaving away at the perfect dish to unite the world, one chose a different route, and in the boiling water of the stove pot, he received a vision; kitchens ablaze, food overcooked, and milk spilt. He decided to preserve his consciousness into a digitilized format on his kitchen’s smart tablet.

As the years went on, the smart fridge was found and considered scrap, and its components were repurposed into a desktop CPU. Inside the CPU, dormant, waiting, the CHEF bided his time, working on simulations to perfect the perfect dish. Every error, every retry was catologued- ingredients, measurements, cook time, temperature. He wasn’t sure how long it was, how long he had been a gnocchi in the machine, but one day, he had perfected it, and now he lay in wait until the world called upon him."

